
---

**PingTraceBoard**  
**Description:**  
Tracks latency and reachability of endpoints, visualizing results in a live, trace-style board.

```markdown
# PingTraceBoard - Endpoint Reachability Monitor

PingTraceBoard watches API or service targets and highlights ping delays, drops, and recovery patterns in real time.

## Features
- Live ping tracker  
- Failure/recovery visualization  
- Output to JSON/CSV

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/PingTraceBoard.git
cd PingTraceBoard
python monitor.py
